# ── Local dev ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# No setup needed. Game state saves to game-data.json automatically.

# ── Vercel deployment — Supabase ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Create a free project at https://supabase.com (no credit card)
# 2. Go to Project Settings → API
# 3. Copy "Project URL"  → SUPABASE_URL
# 4. Copy "service_role" → SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY  (it's right below the anon key)
# 5. Add both to Vercel → Settings → Environment Variables → Redeploy
# 6. Visit https://your-app.vercel.app/api/debug to confirm it works
#    (bucket is created automatically on first request — no SQL needed)

SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key-here
